PN,40401
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1784045921
OL,3,CMore than 300 deaths in the South West
OL,4,C'linked to heatwaves'
OL,6,FThere were more than 300 deaths in the
OL,7,FSouth West linked to the recent
OL,8,Fheatwaves, according to experts.
OL,10,FResearchers from Imperial College
OL,11,FLondon, the Met Office, and the London
OL,12,FSchool of Hygiene and Tropical
OL,13,FMedicine (LSHTM) estimated that there
OL,14,Fwere 319 excess deaths in the South
OL,15,FWest over May and June.
OL,17,FThe South West's ambulance service had
OL,18,Fthe busiest day on record during the
OL,19,FJune heatwave.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1784045921
OL,3,CMore than 300 deaths in the South West
OL,4,C'linked to heatwaves'
OL,6,FOn 25 June, South Western Ambulance
OL,7,FService NHS Trust (SWAST) received
OL,8,Fover 5,200 calls to its emergency
OL,9,Fcontrol rooms and handled more than
OL,10,F4,300 incidents across the region,
OL,11,Fwhich was placed under a red heat
OL,12,Fhealth alert.
OL,14,FMeanwhile, the amber heat health
OL,15,Fwarning issued by the UK Health
OL,16,FSecurity Agency (UKHSA) for the South
OL,17,FWest was due to end on Sunday evening,
OL,18,Fbut is now in place until 9pm on
OL,19,FWednesday 15 July.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1784045921
OL,3,CMore than 300 deaths in the South West
OL,4,C'linked to heatwaves'
OL,6,FThis means significant impacts are
OL,7,Flikely across health and social care
OL,8,Fservices due to the high temperatures,
OL,9,Fincluding a rise in deaths,
OL,10,Fparticularly among those aged 65 and
OL,11,Fover, or with health conditions.
OL,13,FAcross the UK, experts estimated there
OL,14,Fwere 2,700 excess deaths in England
OL,15,Fand Wales over the two heatwaves.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1784045921
OL,3,CMore than 300 deaths in the South West
OL,4,C'linked to heatwaves'
OL,6,FThe research also found that climate
OL,7,Fchange significantly drove up the
OL,8,Fdeath toll, as more than two fifths
OL,9,F(42%) died as a result of the extra
OL,10,Fheat caused by human activity ` mostly
OL,11,Fburning fossil fuels.
OL,13,FTheir study, which used peer-reviewed
OL,14,Fmethods to deliver near rapid
OL,15,Festimates of deaths, examined the
OL,16,Fperiods around the record-breaking
OL,17,Fheatwaves of May, when temperatures
OL,18,Fpeaked at 35.1C, and June, which hit
OL,19,Fnew highs for the month of above 37C,
OL,20,Faccompanied by high humidity.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1784045921
OL,3,CMore than 300 deaths in the South West
OL,4,C'linked to heatwaves'
OL,6,FThe analysis used weather data,
OL,7,Fclimate models and heat-related deaths
OL,8,Fresearch to estimate the number of
OL,9,Fpeople who died in the heatwaves, and
OL,10,Fcompare it to how many lives would
OL,11,Fhave been lost in a climate that had
OL,12,Fnot been warmed by human activities.
OL,14,FThe analysis found about 550 people
OL,15,Fare estimated to have died because of
OL,16,Fheat-related causes in nine days of
OL,17,Fthe May heatwave, and about 2,200 in
OL,18,Fthe 11 days around the June heatwave
OL,19,Fin England and Wales.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1784045921
OL,3,CMore than 300 deaths in the South West
OL,4,C'linked to heatwaves'
OL,6,FAround 59% of the deaths in May, some
OL,7,F327 people, and 38%, some 825 people,
OL,8,Fof those in June could be attributed
OL,9,Fto the extra heat caused by climate
OL,10,Fchange, they found.
OL,12,FThe researchers warn maximum daytime
OL,13,Ftemperatures are around 3C-4C hotter
OL,14,Fthan they would be without climate
OL,15,Fchange, raising the risks from the
OL,16,Fheat.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1784045921
OL,3,CMore than 300 deaths in the South West
OL,4,C'linked to heatwaves'
OL,6,FHigh temperatures are associated with
OL,7,Frisks including heat exhaustion, heat
OL,8,Fstroke, stress on the heart and
OL,9,Fkidneys and worsening chronic
OL,10,Fconditions such as heart disease, lung
OL,11,Fconditions and diabetes.
OL,13,FThey also worsen mental health,
OL,14,Fviolence and increase the risk of
OL,15,Fdeath from drowning.
OL,17,FThe Met Office's Dr Mark McCarthy
OL,18,Fdescribed the two record-breaking
OL,19,Fheatwaves as "exceptional".
OL,26,@{D@NOU{D@ZO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1784045921
OL,3,CMore than 300 deaths in the South West
OL,4,C'linked to heatwaves'
OL,6,FHe said heatwave thresholds were
OL,7,Frarely met in May, but this year
OL,8,Fdaytime temperatures were widely 15C
OL,9,Fabove the average for the month in
OL,10,FEngland and Wales, while night-time
OL,11,Ftemperature records were also set.
OL,13,FThe June heatwave, which saw red
OL,14,Fwarnings for extreme heat issued on
OL,15,Fconsecutive days, was notable for its
OL,16,Fhumidity as well as heat, he said.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1784045921
OL,3,CMore than 300 deaths in the South West
OL,4,C'linked to heatwaves'
OL,6,F"They were extreme heatwaves for the
OL,7,FUK, and for all parts of western
OL,8,FEurope, and they're particularly
OL,9,Fexceptional for the timing and how
OL,10,Fearly in the year they occurred.
OL,12,F"This combination of extreme daytime
OL,13,Fheat, high humidity and hot nights all
OL,14,Fact to really contribute and increase
OL,15,Fthe impact these heatwaves have on our
OL,16,Finfrastructure, on transport,
OL,17,Fagriculture and particularly on our
OL,18,Fhealth and well being," he said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUzD@WO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1784045921
OL,3,CMore than 300 deaths in the South West
OL,4,C'linked to heatwaves'
OL,6,FIt was clear climate change is making
OL,7,Fheatwaves more frequent and intense,
OL,8,Fhe said.
OL,10,FDr Clair Barnes from Imperial College
OL,11,FLondon, said heatwaves are the "most
OL,12,Fdangerous kind of extreme weather",
OL,13,Fwith the World Health Organisation
OL,14,Frecommending authorities in Europe
OL,15,Fplan for extreme heat in the same way
OL,16,Fthey do for winter flu.
OL,26,@sD@`OUtD@bO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1784045921
OL,3,CMore than 300 deaths in the South West
OL,4,C'linked to heatwaves'
OL,6,FShe warned that while heatwaves
OL,7,Fprompted news images of people eating
OL,8,Fice cream and sunbathing on beaches,
OL,9,F"people need to be aware that we are
OL,10,Fnow seeing dangerous climate-change
OL,11,Ffuelled heat that is claiming lives,
OL,12,Fdisrupting schools and hospitals and
OL,13,Fshutting down transport and
OL,14,Finfrastructure".
OL,16,F"It's time we woke up to the fact that
OL,17,Fwe now live in a country with
OL,18,Fdangerously hot summers.
OL,26,@qD@AOUvD@OO]xD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1784045921
OL,3,CMore than 300 deaths in the South West
OL,4,C'linked to heatwaves'
OL,6,F"To protect people during future
OL,7,Fextremes, we must urgently adapt to
OL,8,Fthe reality of the climate we now
OL,9,Fhave, and double down on global
OL,10,Fefforts to reach net zero emissions to
OL,11,Fstop this from getting worse," she
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@^O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/12
